    <p>{`BooGi gives you powerful diagramming capabilities, allowing you to treat
your graphs / diagrams as a code. To give such possibility, BooGi offers
two diagramming "languages": `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "#mermaiddiagrams"
      }}>{`Mermaid`}</a>{` and `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "#graphvizgraphs"
      }}>{`Graphviz`}</a>{`.
Both process Mermaid process markdown code blocks to generate graphs during
page build time.`}</p>
    <section><h2 parentName="section">{`Mermaid diagrams`}</h2><p parentName="section">{`Mermaid can be used to create UML and non-UML diagrams, such as:`}</p><ul parentName="section">
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/flowchart"
          }}>{`flowcharts`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/sequenceDiagram"
          }}>{`sequence diagrams`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/classDiagram"
          }}>{`class diagrams`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/stateDiagram"
          }}>{`state diagrams`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/entityRelationshipDiagram"
          }}>{`entity relationship diagrams (ERD)`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/user-journey"
          }}>{`user journey maps`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/gantt"
          }}>{`gantt diagrams`}</a></li>
        <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/pie"
          }}>{`pie charts`}</a></li>
      </ul><p parentName="section">{`Mermaid offers a way to create even complex diagrams. To create a diagram,
