            "href": "https://mermaid-js.github.io/mermaid/#/"
          }}>{`this guide`}</a>{` (go to
`}<em parentName="p">{`Diagrams`}</em>{` section to find syntax you're looking for).`}</p></Info><p parentName="section">{`Mermaid diagrams can be additionally configured in BooGi page config,
as described in `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "/configuration/setting-up/features#mermaidgraphs"
        }}>{`features reference`}</a>{`.`}</p><p parentName="section"><strong parentName="p">{`Example:`}</strong></p><pre parentName="section"><code parentName="pre" {...{
